1
00:01:05,792 --> 00:01:08,288
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

2
00:01:08,288 --> 00:01:11,296
=Episode 7=

3
00:01:14,349 --> 00:01:17,888
(Xunfang Pavilion)

4
00:01:18,719 --> 00:01:19,439
Search.

5
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,040
Unfortunate.

6
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:43,319
We're closed for business today.

7
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,200
Your Highness should come another day.

8
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,599
I'm not here for entertainment today.

9
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,920
I have questions for you.

10
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:55,079
Is this spice from this place?

11
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,400
So what if it is?

12
00:02:00,959 --> 00:02:03,280
But the ingredients
are exclusive to Dada.

13
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:05,840
You have remarkable reach.

14
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:09,680
Running a business requires
diverse connections.

15
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:12,360
Since customers adore spices from Dada,

16
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,120
we must get them.

17
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,439
But this spice was found

18
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:17,479
on the assassin
who targeted His Majesty.

19
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,439
How do you explain that?

20
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,000
Assassins are men too.

21
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,639
Men are notoriously fickle,

22
00:02:26,639 --> 00:02:28,080
frequenting pleasure quarters.

23
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,680
Isn't that normal?

24
00:02:32,319 --> 00:02:33,919
When did I ever say

25
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,840
the assassin was a man?

26
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,240
Or do you

27
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:41,159
discriminate against female assassins?

28
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:47,039
If it were a woman,

29
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:50,879
she might have used my place as cover.

30
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:53,080
That's certainly possible.

31
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:57,199
Your Highness,

32
00:02:57,879 --> 00:02:59,639
these were uncovered in the cellar.

33
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:00,960
It seems

34
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,240
you're close to the assassin,

35
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:06,439
who even entrusted you
with hiding these items.

36
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:10,680
That vile Emperor
is cruel and bloodthirsty!

37
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,560
Everyone wants him dead!

38
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,479
Nonsense!

39
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:16,240
His Majesty governs with benevolence!

40
00:03:16,719 --> 00:03:18,120
How dare you treasonous villain

41
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,280
spout such nonsense?

42
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,639
He killed my family

43
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:21,960
and made me endure torment.

44
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,240
He deserves death!

45
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,080
Jinming mentioned

46
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:29,639
Mudan, mistress
of the Xunfang Pavilion, is not simple.

47
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,120
Even in the prison,

48
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:33,199
she insisted that to avenge her father,

49
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:35,080
she became General Xu's death warrior.

50
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,400
Last time, it was her

51
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,240
slandering my brother
at the Xunfang Pavilion.

52
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,439
When did you go to that place?

53
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,560
Well...

54
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,680
Last time.

55
00:03:48,919 --> 00:03:50,400
Jinming took me there.

56
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:53,560
Your Majesty,

57
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:56,159
Mudan's father was Anchang's prefect.

58
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:58,039
What crime earned him the death penalty?

59
00:03:58,240 --> 00:04:00,039
Corruption and ruthless slaughter.

60
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,599
He massacred a village.

61
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,240
Such an evil man.

62
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,240
It serves him right.

63
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,159
And she wanted revenge?

64
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,639
People and matters are not one-sided.

65
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:10,039
Though brutal to others,

66
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,319
he doted on Mudan.

67
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:14,479
In her eyes,

68
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,279
could he be a villain?

69
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:18,319
Forget it.

70
00:04:18,399 --> 00:04:20,000
I oversimplified it.

71
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,120
No wonder my father and brother

72
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,279
always worry about me.

73
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,560
Xu Yu.

74
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:30,000
Though beauties surround me,

75
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:33,120
none compares to one person.

76
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:36,920
You're that person.

77
00:04:41,319 --> 00:04:43,279
Your vows sound sweet,

78
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,439
but you still keep a harem
of thousands of ladies.

79
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:51,160
If we ever switch back,

80
00:04:52,839 --> 00:04:54,399
would Your Majesty stay true?

81
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:58,680
Xu Yu.

82
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:01,000
I'll take you somewhere.

83
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:10,079
Close your eyes.

84
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,560
Alright.

85
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:21,319
The palace holds such a nice place!

86
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,399
Do you truly like it?

87
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,399
Absolutely.

88
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:31,680
However,

89
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:34,000
when did you build this conservatory?

90
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:35,720
Why have you never told me?

91
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,759
I'm not skilled,

92
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,319
but this conservatory

93
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:41,160
was designed by me alone.

94
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,639
I wanted to give you

95
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:44,519
as our wedding gift.

96
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,680
But with court instability,

97
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,279
new border wars,

98
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:51,279
and Mother being so worried
about me having no one to rely on

99
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,439
that she fell ill,

100
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,759
I had no choice

101
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:54,959
but to halt construction.

102
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,199
Later, I wanted

103
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,839
to give this to you on your birthday.

104
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,160
But...

105
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:00,759
But

106
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:01,759
on that day,

107
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:03,480
we had an unpleasant argument.

108
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,959
I almost raised my hand against you.

109
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,079
The first flower you gave me

110
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,439
was hibiscus.

111
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,879
Do you remember

112
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,480
what you said to me back then?

113
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,759
Garden flowers smile
in youthful splendor.

114
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:30,519
Pond grasses glow with spring's colors.

115
00:06:30,879 --> 00:06:32,360
Yet none compares to the hibiscus.

116
00:06:32,439 --> 00:06:34,240
Graceful by the jade steps.

117
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:36,439
Do you understand the poem's meaning?

118
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:38,519
Anyway, it means

119
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,879
even the finest blooms in your garden

120
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,600
can't match the one in my hand.

121
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:43,720
It's yours now.

122
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:48,399
So,

123
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:51,279
you remember everything from childhood.

124
00:07:13,888 --> 00:07:14,879
Marquis.

125
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,920
Your constant pacing

126
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,600
is making me dizzy.

127
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:22,000
Now that Xunfang Pavilion is sealed,

128
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:24,199
all our intelligence networks
are severed.

129
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,000
I suspect the next move

130
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:28,680
will be Xiao Jinming
putting me into the Supreme Court.

131
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:31,199
Don't panic prematurely.

132
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,839
It'll only hasten your death.

133
00:07:33,879 --> 00:07:35,000
Remember this.

134
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:38,600
The Ministry of Justice and Supreme Court
are watching this case.

135
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:41,040
Our Emperor

136
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,879
wants you to act
recklessly in desperation.

137
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,759
This time,

138
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:57,319
we underestimated
Xiao Jinyun and the Empress.

139
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,759
You acted too hastily, Marquis.

140
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,680
It was you who told Lady Tao

141
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,439
to use her child for favor,

142
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,439
right?

143
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:13,959
You deliberately had her frame Xu Yu

144
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,120
and even found physicians
for her pregnancy,

145
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,519
fearing actual harm to the baby.

146
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,240
What a pity.

147
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,240
You lost more than you gained.

148
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:24,399
The baby was gone.

149
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:27,000
That fool.

150
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,680
I told her to fake it.

151
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,040
I had other plans arranged.

152
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,560
However,

153
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,159
the baby didn't topple the Empress.

154
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,456
The autumn hunt didn't harm
Xiao Jinyun or the Xu family.

155
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:38,559
Instead, it's pushing me toward death.

156
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:41,679
Who told you to act unilaterally?

157
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:43,519
As for the autumn hunt,

158
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:46,159
my father warned you beforehand.

159
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,720
Don't rush critical matters.

160
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:51,679
But you ignored all his advice.

161
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,480
Come here.

162
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:01,320
I'm Feiyang.

163
00:09:01,919 --> 00:09:03,080
Greetings, Marquis.

164
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:05,159
Feiyang will replace Mudan

165
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,519
as head of the new intelligence hub.

166
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,120
Then,

167
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,960
where is it?

168
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:18,240
These details require
no attention from you.

169
00:09:21,759 --> 00:09:24,159
The capital has been rather dull lately.

170
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:28,320
What if bandits storm the city?

171
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:31,279
How many lives will be lost?

172
00:09:53,759 --> 00:09:55,639
I thought you disliked doing this.

173
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,240
Today, I want to do it.

174
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,360
Xu Yu.

175
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,320
I gifted you the conservatory

176
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:08,360
from my sincere heart.

177
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,480
It was my promise to you.

178
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,639
Most importantly,

179
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:14,159
I want your happiness.

180
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,600
No bargains are required.

181
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,039
Nor do I need

182
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:21,480
you forcing yourself
into unpleasant duties.

183
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,440
But as the Empress,

184
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,840
I must learn to do this.

185
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,519
I want to help you.

186
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:30,840
Good.

187
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,120
Understood.

188
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,440
Let me teach you.

189
00:10:34,944 --> 00:10:35,480
Alright.

190
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:42,320
(I'll replace the pain
I caused you in the past)

191
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,584
(with beautiful moments)

192
00:10:43,584 --> 00:10:45,360
(bit by bit.)

193
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:46,720
Look here.

194
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,600
This entry

195
00:10:48,879 --> 00:10:50,039
is recorded as income.

196
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,919
This denotes procurement.

197
00:10:51,919 --> 00:10:52,600
Your Majesty.

198
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,559
Your Majesty.

199
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,840
Lady Tao hanged herself.

200
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,720
You may leave.

201
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,399
A consort's suicide

202
00:11:27,399 --> 00:11:28,919
implicates her entire family.

203
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,200
Moreover,

204
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,759
your uncle is the Marquis of Zhenbei.

205
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,440
Now that you've been rescued,

206
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:35,159
why ask to see me privately?

207
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,879
Do you intend to tell me the truth?

208
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:39,759
Your Majesty.

209
00:11:40,120 --> 00:11:41,799
For your father and brothers' careers,

210
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,879
it must be exhausting to perform

211
00:11:43,879 --> 00:11:45,240
in front of His Majesty.

212
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,960
(If she had said this earlier,)

213
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,320
(I might have believed her.)

214
00:11:49,679 --> 00:11:50,519
(But now,)

215
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:53,080
(I'll only see it
as her sowing discord.)

216
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,840
I'm a general's daughter.

217
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,799
I refuse to learn
your hypocritical ways.

218
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,480
My devotion to His Majesty

219
00:11:58,639 --> 00:12:00,000
is genuine.

220
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,559
Genuine devotion.

221
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,759
What a pity.

222
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:06,879
Not all genuine devotion is cherished.

223
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,279
You're right.

224
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:10,519
A man's heart

225
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,320
is as firm as stone.

226
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,600
You can't move them and earn their love

227
00:12:14,799 --> 00:12:17,039
unless you already occupy their heart.

228
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,399
But those who don't love you

229
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:21,200
only deceive you.

230
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,480
Even innocent infants become pawns

231
00:12:23,799 --> 00:12:25,879
in their power struggles.

232
00:12:31,559 --> 00:12:32,720
Your Majesty.

233
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,919
You're right.

234
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:35,559
I...

235
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:39,600
I will tell you everything I know.

236
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:51,519
What are you doing?

237
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:04,440
Xu Yu!

238
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,799
How dare you!

239
00:13:10,519 --> 00:13:11,320
Mother!

240
00:13:14,559 --> 00:13:16,240
Summon Jiang Tang immediately! Hurry!

241
00:13:16,279 --> 00:13:16,840
Yes.

242
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:17,960
Aunt.

243
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:22,000
I can't believe the Empress
committed violence in the palace!

244
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:22,960
Xu Yu.

245
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,840
His Majesty has favored you
for a few days.

246
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,320
Do you think you're above us all now?

247
00:13:26,639 --> 00:13:28,559
I won't hear any excuses from you.

248
00:13:29,279 --> 00:13:30,519
Regarding Lady Tao's matter,

249
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,440
I'll handle it personally.

250
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:33,519
Guards.

251
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,639
Escort the Empress back
to Fengyi Palace.

252
00:13:35,799 --> 00:13:36,600
Who dares?

253
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,679
Defy my decree?

254
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:38,440
Mother!

255
00:13:38,919 --> 00:13:39,919
I'm concerned.

256
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:40,960
You're above all,

257
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,200
and no one speaks against you,

258
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,559
which may be used by schemers.

259
00:13:45,159 --> 00:13:47,039
Are you questioning my judgment?

260
00:13:47,039 --> 00:13:47,879
Mother!

261
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,960
The reason

262
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,519
you came to see me committing violence

263
00:13:51,399 --> 00:13:53,120
must be that Consort Zhao informed you.

264
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,759
Isn't this manipulation?

265
00:13:55,039 --> 00:13:56,039
Your Majesty!

266
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:57,600
Don't slander me!

267
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,240
Last time, Lady Tao

268
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,080
used her stillborn child to frame me.

269
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,440
You believed it was true then.

270
00:14:02,519 --> 00:14:03,679
Must history

271
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:05,039
repeat itself now?

272
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:07,960
Lady Tao

273
00:14:08,799 --> 00:14:10,279
requested a private meeting here.

274
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:12,279
I thought she'd reveal the truth,

275
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,000
so I let my guard down.

276
00:14:14,759 --> 00:14:16,200
That's how she managed to wound me.

277
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:18,840
(When did Xu Yu become so articulate?)

278
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,519
(Did His Majesty teach her?)

279
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:22,799
You should return
to Fengyi Palace to recuperate first.

280
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:25,840
Thank you for your trust, Mother.

281
00:14:47,410 --> 00:14:52,592
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

282
00:14:53,347 --> 00:14:57,814
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

283
00:14:59,189 --> 00:15:04,320
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

284
00:15:05,112 --> 00:15:09,595
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

285
00:15:10,198 --> 00:15:15,520
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

286
00:15:16,111 --> 00:15:21,750
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

287
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:24,160
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

288
00:15:24,160 --> 00:15:28,096
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

289
00:15:28,448 --> 00:15:33,288
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

290
00:15:33,656 --> 00:15:35,815
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

291
00:15:35,815 --> 00:15:39,744
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

292
00:15:39,744 --> 00:15:44,672
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪
